title: Duran Duran *LIVE* at Wembley Arena
description:
Simon and the boys bring their 80's Hits to the stage in one of the better Wembley concerts of the early 21st Century. Playing to the crowd, the hometown boys include their top sellers like "Rio", "Wild Boys", "The Reflex", "Union of the Snake" and more.

This concert is an HD presentation and capped for your viewing pleasure. This 53 minute (approx) concert is HD Wide Screen and transcoded to avi format.
